title: Under A Dying Sun "Hangman's Day" 2000 *emo* FLAC
description:
The "Hangman's Day" EP from Under A Dying Sun.  Definitely way out-of-print.  Great 90s-wave emo ala Indian Summer, Funeral Diner, and many others.  This was mail-ordered straight from the band way back in the good ol' days. Unfun Records.
